### HTTP Request

`POST https://<%= config[:api_endpoint] %>/otp/send`

Method sends one-time password to authorize bonuses usage on POS. This method sends a code even if recipient is not a member of loyalty program.

| Parameter   | Type   | Required | Description         |
|-------------|--------|----------|---------------------|
| shop_id     | String | true     | Your API key        |
| shop_secret | String | true     | Your API secret key |
| phone       | String | true     | Phone number        |
| event       | String | true     | Event to authorize  |

